parameters: How's that! Did you see that!!!\n< Erika >

How about that! How do you like the
taste of my right arm, Mr. Minotaur!\n< Erika >

Lady Erika... my apologies, I've been
careless.\n< Serena >
You risked your right arm for me...\n< Serena >

...Still alive, are you? Minotaur. Your
vitality is astounding.\n< Serena >

...But with those wounds, you're beyond
saving. If you wish to die quietly, I
won't pursue you...\n< Serena >

...It seems you have no such intention.
Very well.\n< Serena >

My name is Serena. Fuoco. R. Brillante.
Della. Grazia.\n< Serena >

The last bloodline of the ancient
empire... and my proud friend, Erika
Linlert, the sword and shield.\n< Serena >

Minotaur, you soul without refuge, you
evil monster.\n< Serena >

The god who reigns over this world shall
take your life and grant you a shameful
death!\n< Serena >
Come at me if you dare!\n< Serena >
G-guh... Serena! Are you alright? Serena!\n< Erika >
Damn it...! Are you after Serena...?!\n< Erika >

Do you prefer blondes? That's how she
was too, huh...\n< Erika >

Oh god... damn... I think I just messed
up my insides...\n< Erika >

Haa... Ha... Haha... Heehee...
hehehehe... hehe of he...\n< Erika >

Serena's behind me. In front is this
bastard. My body's all battered and
broken here and there.\n< Erika >

Isn't it great, things are really
heating up now.\n< Erika >

Hahahaha! Sorry about that! Interrupting
your meal and all!!\n< Erika >

But you know... there's an order to a
meal. Jumping straight to the main dish
isn't very mannerly.\n< Erika >

You start with the hors d'oeuvres,
that's the proper way to do it... It
might not look great, but this is my
specialty dish...\n< Erika >
I'm confident in its texture!\n< Erika >

What's the matter, bull boy?! You said
you were gonna kill me... I thought
you'd be something special!\n< Erika >

But no!... Your attacks are... light...!
Have you been eating properly...?\n< Erika >

That's right... come at me... don't just
stand there looking...!\n< Erika >

parameters.name: 咀嚼・もぐもぐ・ゆっくり

parameters:
You bastard, my right arm...!! You
bastard---! It hurts so damn much!!\n< Erika >
How dare you!! Eat it, didn't you?!\n< Erika >

The blood is gushing out... This is
bad... I'm seriously gonna die...\n< Erika >
Is this my final stand...\n< Erika >

Hah... you're munching away so
happily... It really pisses me off...!\n< Erika >

At this rate, it'll be like I'm dying
with you, won't it?!\n< Erika >
How about that! Did you see?!!\n< Erika >

How is it! The taste of my right arm!
Mr. Minotaur!\n< Erika >

Gob... hehe... My flesh is... a bit
different from yours, isn't it?!\n< Erika >

...hah... serves you right... Seriously,
today is... the best... day...\n< Erika >

Trash and scum... all cleaned up at
once... It's a refreshing... good
feeling...\n< Erika >

tenacity.\n< Serena >

...But with those wounds, you won't
survive much longer. If you wish to die
quietly, I won't bother chasing you...\n< Serena >

...It seems you don't want that. Very
well.\n< Serena >

My name is Serena. Fuoco. R. Brillante.
D. La. Grazia.\n< Serena >

The last bloodline of the ancient
empire... and my proud friend, Erika
Linluth, the sword and shield.\n< Serena >

Minotaur. A soul with no place to
belong. An evil monster.\n< Serena >

The god who judges this world shall take
your life and grant you a death filled
with shame!\n< Serena >
Come at me if you dare!\n< Serena >

Ugh... I'm out of magical power...
Forgive me, Lady Erika...\n< Serena >

What now...? To die in a place like
this...?\n< Serena >
No no no. No! Nooo!\n< Serena >
I don't want to! No! ...Mother--\n< Serena >

咀嚼・もぐもぐ・ゆっくり

parameters:
...Sound, that is. Vibration, that is.
Impact.\n< Serena >

I've turned your body into an
instrument. The melody of flesh tearing,
the rhythm of bones breaking.\n< Serena >

Sound begets sound, impact begets
impact. There's no stopping it now.\n< Serena >

Die to the funeral march played by your
own body.\n< Serena >

Perhaps that was too reckless... But
this is no time to falter.\n< Serena >

Let's return, Lady Erika. It's alright.
I will surely find a way.\n< Serena >
I cannot afford to have you die on me.\n< Serena >
After all, you are my second friend...\n< Serena >
